ka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gene-wilder-as-Willy-Wonka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gene-wilder-as-Willy-Wonka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gene-wilder-as-Willy-Wonka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gene-wilder-as-Willy-Wonka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gene-wilder-as-Willy-Wonka-Photo-by-Silver-Screen-Collection_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部关于近期《威利旺卡》体验的新纪录片将于下周在第五频道播出。</p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wonka-review-timothee-chalamet-3553138">《旺卡》评论：蒂莫西·查拉梅 (Timothée Chalamet) 在充满乐趣的节日盛宴中闪闪发光</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部一次性纪录片将记录上个月在格拉斯哥发生的灾难性事件，该事件<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/flop-willy-wonka-experience-in-glasgow-goes-viral-for-being-so-terrible-3593684">在社交媒体上疯传</a>。</p><p>广告宣传为“甜蜜和想象力的庆典”，其灵感来自热门电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka"><i>《旺卡</i></a>》及其背后的罗尔德·达尔书籍，愤怒的家长在上映后不久就开始要求退款，并将其描述为“牛仔”上演的“闹剧”。该活动的组织者光明会之家在开幕仅几个小时后就决定终止活动。</p><p>第五频道现已向<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/willy-wonka-experience-documentary-channel-5-b2508072.html"><i>《独立报》</i></a>证实，他们将制作一部独立纪录片，名为<i>《威利·旺卡：震惊英国的丑闻》</i> 。该广播公司尚未确认该节目的概要，仅表示该节目将由 Mentorn Media 制作。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="旺卡 |官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/otNh9bTjXWg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在此消息发布之前，参加活动的演员之一<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/willy-wonka-experience-uk-glasgow-scam-b2504130.html?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR0HyEbWmI8mvRDeO-NbrWw7odEUQ6uUa93w9kJnt5_YwBwBPeakPjtm3yA#Echobox=1709158821">科斯蒂·帕特森 (Kirsty Paterson) 此前曾公开讲述了这次灾难性的经历</a>，并透露她尚未收到为演出提供的 500 英镑报酬。</p><p> “整件事简直就是一团糟。老实说，这令人震惊，”她告诉<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-13131605/willy-wonka-scam-embarrassed-actress-memorise-ai-script-not-paid.html"><i>《每日邮报》</i></a> 。</p><p>后来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/willys-chocolate-factory-experience-wonka-actor-speaks-out-about-dangerous-and-heartbreaking-event-3594918">被雇来模仿威利·旺卡的演员之一保罗·康奈尔透露了更多有关灾难性事件如何发生的信息。</a> “剧本是由人工智能生成的 15 页胡言乱语，我只是在独白这些疯狂的事情，”他告诉<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/willy-wonka-experience-glasgow-chocolate-event-b2504464.html"><i>《独立报》</i></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sydney-sweeney-mocks-glasgows-wonka-experience-in-snl-skit-3596176">西德尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 最近在<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目中表演小品时也对这一活动进行了取笑</a>。</p><p> <i>《威利·旺卡：震惊英国的丑闻》</i>将于 3 月 16 日在第五频道播出。</p><p>即将 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/willy-wonka-experience-documentary-to-air-on-channel-5-3598154">在第五频道播出的《威利旺卡体验》纪录片</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ;
